    "Boolean operators (AND, OR) were used to narrow the search and create search strings by combining the keywords.",
    "After conducting a comprehensive search of the six databases, titles and abstracts of the resulting articles were screened and selected for inclusion.",
    "Literature management software (Mendeley; Elsevier) was used to remove duplicates and organize the identified publications.",
    "The screening process involved reviewing the titles, abstracts, and full-text articles.",
    "Only publications published in English with accessible abstracts were included."
